- When `git describe` fails to retrieve a tag, the resulting log/error message now includes all options passed to the command (based on contribution by [@jenshnielsen](https://github.com/jenshnielsen))
- When `hg log` fails to retrieve a tag, the resulting log/error message now includes the tag pattern passed to `latesttag()`, if any

- Support using the `onbuild` step with Hatch
